    <h4 class="docs-mb-4">What is ember-phone-input?</h4>

    <p>It is an ember.js addon: a component backed by a service.</p>
    <p>The component provides easy input / validation of international phone numbers. The service takes care of loading the scripts.</p>
    <p>It wraps the well maintained javascript package: <a href="https://github.com/jackocnr/intl-tel-input" target="_blank">intl-tel-input</a>, itself based on Google's <a href="https://github.com/googlei18n/libphonenumber" target="_blank">libphonenumber library</a>.</p>

